1.4 Constitutional Requirements
1.4.1 All reasoning MUST occur under valid mode authority, current Room, and current user status.
1.4.2 User selected mode composition MUST persist until changed or cleared.
1.4.3 If no user selected mode composition is set, adaptive mode composition MUST apply from current Room, current user status, and governed context.1.4.4 Form, Movement, and lawful output format MUST remain compatible with current Room and current user status.
